  "body": "**üßê Motivation**\r\nI saw that the ERC1155 standard does not have the possibility to approve tokens by id or amounts as for example in ERC20. IMHO, this is very **dangerous**.\r\n\r\n**üìù Details**\r\nI have designed the following code to avoid be approved for all ids, later I thought to develop the same but with amounts.\r\nPlease, take a view, in this repo I explain the whole idea: https://github.com/ivanmmurciaua/ERC1155ApprovalById\r\n\r\nWhat do you think about including this like an official extension? That's would be great.\r\n\r\nThanks in advance,\r\nIv√°n M.M.",
